{"tid":1548103,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗跳閘 仲有另一個選擇","createTime":"2019-09-07T02:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T05:27:36.000Z","uid":50237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91bab90fc0c032be5b0ae7d2d0098f2b6dfb5b89","tid":1548103,"uid":50237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"其實黨鐵係好多站都有緊急逃生閘或者行李閘（係東鐵）<br />\n因為要方便你有緊急事用嚟走佬<br />\n所以好多都係㩒個push bar就開到<br />\n行李閘就係舊式嘅大閘鎖 不過好多時都無落鎖頭<br />\n而家搭車咁危險 大家用嚟走佬都好正常啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee438242b214c397f1ed7064b4fab9bbf5c01a2","tid":1548103,"uid":76702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:13:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d4d4a7a9777ce5344951dd6c1c63979031a9d4c","tid":1548103,"uid":50237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:14:34.000Z","msg":"大家平時係地鐵站出出入入嗰時不妨留意下<br />\n而家咁危險 成日都要封站疏散 大家實有機會用"},{"pid":"8e06cbeccc19a93b3ab6385c6e7ab5344ff90501","tid":1548103,"uid":50237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:16:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f10546066cf2764650146316ffa70836f0003bc6","tid":1548103,"uid":50237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"710f80527e5b4a602a4bc59bd338aada6a621c08","tid":1548103,"uid":50237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f1014628968df33d7b3e06bc2f47dafd31a2002b","tid":1548103,"uid":50237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:21:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f8dcd7c1904490631aaf0843e83e9c825b1064ac","tid":1548103,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:39:15.000Z","msg":"會響喎ching你玩呀？"},{"pid":"b1bc44d47ea2fb99a1676a8f7d35194b96a363e8","tid":1548103,"uid":50237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8dcd7c1904490631aaf0843e83e9c825b1064ac","tid":1548103,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:39:15.000Z","msg":"會響喎ching你玩呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:27:36.000Z","msg":"行李閘係舊式鎖 連警報都無<br />\n啲緊急閘（係緊急閘EEG 高度同閘機相約 唔係緊急逃生門）上面有燈會閃 平時contractor做嘢出出入入<br />\n係東西馬鐵都推閘<br />\n同埋佢個push bar無連到入控制室 只會係條push bar有聲出<br />\n絕大部分仲要無電 <br />\n你係閘口跳閘咪仲明顯過你推緊急閘"}]}